efforts of others, freely given with no request for compensation.  

I can't afford Motif on my linux box at home either, but I'd rather be
able to get everyone I work with fired up about W3 than to just play
with it at home over a 14.4K modem.  Where I work all we have are,
suprise, commercial systems.  The Sun's run X, and the PC's run
Windows.
